name: Box of handcrafted fine chocolates
description:
A box of sixteen chocolates hand made in the Yarra Valley by Grace & Paige. Using finest quality couverture chocolate and European techniques, these chocolates are a truly indulgent gift.
Other sizes available on request, price includes delivery, wrapping and hand written card.
